ueSuffix": "B",\n                "yAxisLabel": "Volume (Tỷ USD)"\n              }\n            } -->\n            <div id="volume-bar-chart-container-en" class="chart-container" aria-label="Market Trading Volume Chart"></div>\n            <div class="chart-text-analysis">\n                <p>Total 24-hour market trading volume reached <strong>$274.6 billion USD</strong>. BTC trading volume recently increased by 32%, accompanied by net outflows of <strong>$78.50M</strong> from exchanges, a positive sign of accumulation by large investors.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>\n\n<section id="institutional-whale-analysis-section">\n    <h2><i class="fas fa-building" style="color: var(--icon-color-market-activity);"></i> Institutional Flows & Whale Analysis</h2>\n    <div class="content-grid">\n        <div class="report-card">\n            <h3>Bitcoin & Ether ETF Data</h3>\n            <p>The SEC approved in-kind creation/redemption mechanisms for Bitcoin and Ether ETFs by late July 2025, enhancing efficiency and attracting institutional interest. Spot Bitcoin ETFs recorded over <strong>$404 million USD</strong> in recent inflows. Spot Ether ETFs also saw their second-largest historical inflow: <strong>$729 million USD</strong>.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class="report-card">\n            <h3>Whale & Corporate Activity</h3>\n            <p>Net outflows of <strong>$78.50M</strong> BTC from exchanges on August 14th indicate accumulation by large investors and a reduction in selling supply. MicroStrategy continues to accumulate aggressively, holding over <strong>628,900 BTC</strong> (valued at nearly $76 billion USD) as of August 11, 2025, with an average purchase price of <strong>$66,384.56</strong>. The company acquired an additional 11,931 BTC in August.</p>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>\n\n<section id="macro-analysis-section">\n    <h2><i class="fas fa-globe" style="color: var(--icon-color-macro-legal);"></i> Macro & Regulatory Analysis</h2>\n    <div class="report-card wide-card">\n        <p>JPMorgan notes a weak correlation between the crypto market and Fed interest rates but predicts Bitcoin will outperform gold in H2 2025. Regarding the regulatory framework, the SEC's "Project Crypto" (announced July 31, 2025) aims to modernize the regulatory framework, clarify asset classification, and encourage innovation. The Federal Reserve withdrew its 2022 supervisory guidance on bank crypto activities (April 2025), removing barriers to bank participation. These moves indicate a shift from an enforcement-first approach to an encouraging regulatory framework.</p>\n    </div>\n</section>\n\n<section id="top-coins-analysis-section">\n    <h2><i class="fas fa-coins" style="color: var(--icon-color-eth-analysis);"></i> Top Coins & Trends Analysis</h2>\n    <div class="table-container">\n        <table class="crypto-table">\n            <thead>\n                <tr>\n                    <th>Rank</th>\n                    <th>Coin</th>\n                    <th>Price</th>\n                    <th>24h Change</th>\n                    <th>Market Cap</th>\n                    <th>Volume (24h)</th>\n                </tr>\n            </thead>\n            <tbody>\n                <tr>\n                    <td data-label="Rank">#1</td>\n                    <td data-label="Coin">Bitcoin (BTC)</td>\n                    <td data-label="Price">$118,560.00</td>\n                    <td data-label="24h Change" style="color: var(--negative-color);">-1.71%</td>\n                    <td data-label="Market Cap">$2.33T</td>\n                    <td data-label="Volume (24h)">$80.0B</td>\n                </tr>\n                <tr>\n                    <td data-label="Rank">#2</td>\n                    <td data-label="Coin">Ethereum (ETH)</td>\n                    <td data-label="Price">$4,600.00</td>\n                    <td data-label="24h Change" style="color: var(--positive-color);">+3.15%</td>\n                  