 Conclusion & Recommendations</h2>\n    <div class="report-card wide-card">\n        <p>The cryptocurrency market is in a strong growth phase, supported by regulatory clarity, institutional inflows, and positive sentiment.</p>\n        <h3>Short-term Outlook (1-4 weeks)</h3>\n        <ul>\n            <li><strong>Bullish:</strong> Bitcoin may continue its upward momentum, testing <strong>$126,785 - $128,000</strong>.</li>\n            <li><strong>Sideways:</strong> May consolidate around <strong>$118,000 - $122,000</strong> after a strong rally.</li>\n            <li><strong>Bearish:</strong> Minor corrections may occur, with key support at <strong>$120,450 - $120,470</strong> and <strong>$118,500</strong>. Any dips could present buying opportunities.</li>\n        </ul>\n        <h3>Medium-term Outlook (1-3 months)</h3>\n        <p>Very optimistic. The approval of in-kind mechanisms for ETFs and a clear regulatory framework will continue to attract institutional capital.</p>\n        <h3>Long-term Vision (6-12 months)</h3>\n        <p>Extremely optimistic. Huge growth potential based on expert price predictions, technological advancements (Layer 2, DeFi), and ecosystem maturity.</p>\n        <h3>Risk Assessment</h3>\n        <ul>\n            <li><strong>High Volatility:</strong> The market remains highly volatile.</li>\n            <li><strong>Regulatory Risk:</strong> Unexpected policy changes could cause volatility.</li>\n            <li><strong>Black Swan Events:</strong> Always a potential risk.</li>\n        </ul>\n    </div>\n</section>\n\n<section id="data-validation-section">\n    <h2><i class="fas fa-clipboard-check" style="color: var(--positive-color);"></i> Data Validation</h2>\n    <div class="report-card wide-card">\n        <p>The report has been successfully validated. All critical data perfectly matches the provided real-time data.</p>\n        <div class="table-container">\n            <table class="crypto-table">\n                <thead>\n       