 to ease.</p>\n    </div>\n</section>\n\n<section id="top-coins-analysis-section">\n    <h2 class="section-title"><i class="fab fa-bitcoin" style="color: var(--icon-color-btc-analysis);"></i> Top Coins Analysis</h2>\n    <div class="content-grid">\n        <div class="report-card">\n            <h3>Bitcoin (BTC)</h3>\n            <!-- CHART_DATA: {\n              "type": "line",\n              "data": [117000, 118500, 124000, 118248, 119000],\n              "options": {\n                "color": "var(--icon-color-btc)",\n                "valuePrefix": "$",\n                "valueSuffix": ""\n              }\n            } -->\n            <div id="btc-price-line-chart-container-en" class="chart-container" aria-label="Bitcoin Price Trend Line Chart"></div>\n            <p>Reached a new ATH above <strong>$124,000</strong>, driven by ETF inflows, institutional accumulation, and Fed expectations.</p>\n            <p>Current price: <strong>$118,248</strong> (down 2.43% in 24h).</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class="report-card">\n            <h3>Ethereum (ETH)</h3>\n            <!-- CHART_DATA: {\n              "type": "line",\n              "data": [4700, 4750, 4780, 4760, 4800],\n              "options": {\n                "color": "var(--icon-color-eth)",\n                "valuePrefix": "$",\n                "valueSuffix": ""\n              }\n            } -->\n            <div id="eth-price-line-chart-container-en" class="chart-container" aria-label="Ethereum Price Trend Line Chart"></div>\n            <p>Surged to <strong>$4,780</strong> (up 2.87% in 24h), approaching record price levels.</p>\n            <p>Vibrant DeFi and Layer 2 ecosystems. Expectations for a Spot Ethereum ETF with liquid staking features are driving positive sentiment.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class="report-card wide-card">\n            <h3>Major Altcoins & Emerging Trends</h3>\n            <ul>\n                <li>Solana (SOL), XRP, BNB, TRON all increased by 2.1% to 4%.</li>\n                <li>The SEC's review of the Spot Solana ETF filing indicates interest in solid foundational altcoins.</li>\n                <li><strong>Emerging Trends:</strong> AI, RWA, Gaming (GameFi), SocialFi, and Layer 2 solutions for Bitcoin are gaining attention.</li>\n            </ul>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>\n\n<section id="breaking-news-impact-section">\n    <h2 class="section-title"><i class="fas fa-newspaper" style="color: var(--icon-color-market-activity);"></i> Breaking News & Impact</h2>\n    <div class="report-card wide-card">\n        <dl class="news-impact-list">\n            <dt>Bitcoin sets new ATH above 124,000 USD:</dt>\n            <dd><span class="impact-level high">EXTREMELY HIGH Impact</span>, triggering euphoric sentiment.</dd>\n\n            <dt>SEC concludes Ripple lawsuit and moves towards clear regulatory framework:</dt>\n            <dd><span class="impact-level high">EXTREMELY HIGH Impact</span>, reducing long-term legal risks for the industry.</dd>\n\n            <dt>"Prehistoric whale" activity:</dt>\n            <dd><span class="impact-level medium">MEDIUM Impact</span>, causing short-term price dips but not altering the trend.</dd>\n\n            <dt>MicroStrategy continues BTC purchases:</dt>\n            <dd><span class="impact-level medium">MEDIUM Impact</span>, reinforcing confidence in institutional long-term strategy.</dd>\n\n            <dt>SEC accepts Solana ETF filing:</dt>\n            <dd><span class="impact-level medium">MEDIUM Impact</span>, expanding ETF products to altcoins.</dd>\n        </dl>\n    </div>\n</section>\n\n<section id="expert-opinion-section">\n    <h2 class="section-title"><i class="fas fa-user-tie" style="color: var(--icon-color-expert-outlook);"></i> Expert Opinion</h2>\n    <div class="report-card wide-card">\n        <ul>\n            <li><strong>Tom Lee (Fundstrat):</strong> Predicts Bitcoin price could reach <strong>$250,000</strong> by end of 2025.</li>\n            <li><strong>