rd">\n                <h3>Hệ sinh thái Phương tiện Đầu tư</h3>\n                <p>ARK Invest của Cathie Wood đã mua hơn 2,5 triệu cổ phiếu của Bullish (sàn giao dịch crypto toàn cầu), thể hiện niềm tin vào cơ sở hạ tầng tài sản kỹ thuật số và đã đầu tư vào các dịch vụ staking Ethereum.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id="macro-analysis-section" class="report-section">\n        <h2><i class="fas fa-globe-americas" style="color: var(--icon-color-macro-legal);"></i> Phân tích Vĩ mô Chuyên sâu</h2>\n        <div class="content-grid">\n            <div class="report-card">\n                <h3>Chính sách Fed và Tác động</h3>\n                <p>JPMorgan dự báo Fed sẽ cắt giảm lãi suất 5 lần, bắt đầu từ tháng 9 năm 2025 (25 điểm cơ bản/lần), do thị trường lao động suy yếu. Kỳ vọng này đã thúc đẩy Bitcoin lên mức cao kỷ lục. Lạm phát (CPI cốt lõi tháng 6: 2,6-2,8%) vẫn là mối lo ngại.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class="report-card">\n                <h3>Bối cảnh Quy định</h3>\n                <ul>\n                    <li><strong>SEC:</strong> Đã đưa ra hướng dẫn về staking thanh khoản (5/8/2025), lưu ý một số hình thức nằm ngoài luật chứng khoán. Khởi động "Project Crypto" (1/8/2025) nhằm hiện đại hóa quy định.</li>\n                    <li><strong>CLARITY Act:</strong> Hạ viện thông qua (17/7/2025), cấp thêm quyền hạn cho CFTC đối với giao dịch crypto, đang được Thượng viện xem xét.</li>\n                    <li><strong>Ripple-SEC:</strong> Hạn chót 15/8 cho báo cáo cập nhật chung, khả năng giải quyết 50 triệu USD và dỡ bỏ lệnh cấm bán XRP cho tổ chức.</li>\n                </ul>\n            </div>\n            <div class="report-card">\n                <h3>Các Chỉ số Kinh tế Vĩ mô</h3>\n                <p>PPI tháng 7 của Mỹ tăng mạnh nhất trong ba năm, làm giảm nhẹ kỳ vọng cắt giảm lãi suất. Căng thẳng địa chính trị (Iran, Mỹ-Trung) có thể gây áp lực ngắn hạn.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class="report-card">\n                <h3>Thanh khoản Toàn cầu & Dòng vốn</h3>\n                <p>Sự mở rộng của BRICS và xu hướng phi đô la hóa có thể mở ra cơ hội cho các hệ thống thay thế như tiền điện tử.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id="top-coins-analysis-section" class="report-section">\n        <h2><i class="fas fa-coins" style="color: var(--icon-color-market-activity);"></i> Phân tích Top Coins Chi tiết</h2>\n        <div class="content-grid">\n            <div class="report-card">\n                <h3><i class="fab fa-bitcoin" style="color: var(--icon-color-btc);"></i> Bitcoin (BTC)</h3>\n                <p>Giao dịch quanh <strong>119.118 USD</strong> sau khi đạt đỉnh lịch sử và điều chỉnh. Các yếu tố cơ bản (tích lũy cá voi, dòng tiền tổ chức) vẫn mạnh mẽ. Hash rate và độ khó khai thác ổn định.</p>\n                <!-- CHART_DATA: {\n                  "type": "line",\n                  "data": [118000, 120000, 124457, 119118, 117000, 119500],\n                  "options": {\n                    "color": "var(--icon-color-btc)",\n                    "valuePrefix": "$",\n                    "valueSuffix": ""\n                  }\n                } -->\n                <div id="btc-price-line-chart-container" class="chart-container" aria-label="Bitcoin Price Line Chart"></div>\n            </div>\n            <div class="report-card">\n                <h3><i class="fab fa-ethereum" style="color: var(--icon-color-eth);"></i> Ethereum (ETH)</h3>\n                <p>Giao dịch quanh <strong>4.568 USD</strong>, giảm <span style="color: var(--negative-color);">3,13%</span> trong 24 giờ. Đạt mức cao gần 4.700 USD vào ngày 14/8. Việc Quỹ Ethereum bán 2.795 ETH gây tranh cãi. Phân tích kỹ thuật cho thấy ETH đang ở điều kiện quá mua. Hệ sinh thái mạnh mẽ (96,6 tỷ USD TVL) nhưng đối mặt cạnh tranh từ Layer 2 và Layer 1 khác.</p>\n                <!-- CHART_DATA: {\n                  "type": "line",\n                  "data": [4500, 4600, 4700, 4568, 4450, 4580],\n                  "options": {\n                    "color": "var(--icon-color-eth)",\n                    "valuePrefix": "$",\n                    "valueSuffix": ""\n                  }\n                } -->\n                <div id="eth-price-line-chart-container" class="chart-container" aria-label="Ethereum Price Line Chart"></div>\n            </div>\n            <div class="report-card">\n                <h3><i class="fas fa-chart-area" style="color: var(--accent-color);"></i> Các Altcoin Lớn</h3>\n                <p>Hầu hết các altcoin lớn như XRP, SOL, BNB, DOGE, SUI đều giảm giá, phản ánh sự điều chỉnh trên diện rộng của thị trường.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class="report-card">\n                <h3><i class="fas fa-trending-up" style="color: var(--icon-color-outlook);"></i> Xu hướng mới nổi</h3>\n                <p>AI, Real-World Assets (RWA), Gaming, và Social tokens tiếp tục thu hút sự chú ý.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id="breaking-news-section" class="report-section">\n        <h2><i class="fas fa-newspaper" style="color: var(--icon-color-macro-legal);"></i> Tin Tức Breaking & Phân tích Tác động</h2>\n        <div class="content-grid">\n            <div class="report-card">\n                <h3>Tuyên bố Bộ trưởng Tài chính Mỹ</h3>\n                <p>Scott Bessent khẳng định Washington sẽ không mua thêm Bitcoin cho kho dự trữ chiến lược, gây ra đợt lao dốc bất ngờ của BTC.</p>\n                <p><strong>Tác động:</strong> Cao (8/10) - Ảnh hưởng trực tiếp đến tâm lý và giá BTC.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class="report-card">\n                <h3>Giao dịch ETH của Quỹ Ethereum</h3>\n                <p>Bán 2.795 ETH (127 triệu USD), gây tranh cãi về thời điểm và tính minh bạch.</p>\n                <p><strong>Tác động:</strong> Trung bình (6/10) - Gây áp lực bán ngắn hạn cho ETH.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class="report-card">\n                <h3>Mua Bitcoin của Strategy (MicroStrategy)</h3>\n                <p>Tiếp tục mua thêm 155 BTC, nâng tổng số lên hơn 628.900 BTC.</p>\n                <p><strong>Tác động:</strong> Trung bình (7/10) - Củng cố niềm tin dài hạn.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class="report-card">\n                <h3>IPO của Bullish và đầu tư của Cathie Wood</h3>\n                <p>Sàn giao dịch Bullish ra mắt trên NYSE, cổ phiếu tăng 84%, ARK Invest mua hơn 2,5 triệu cổ phiếu.</p>\n                <p><strong>Tác động:</strong> Trung bình (6/10) - Tín hiệu tích cực cho cơ sở hạ tầng crypto và chấp nhận tổ chức.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id="expert-sentiment-section" class="report-section">\n        <h2><i class="fas fa-comment-dots" style="color: var(--icon-color-expert-outlook);"></i> Ý kiến Chuyên gia & Sentiment Đa chiều</h2>\n        <div class="content-grid">\n            <div class="report-card">\n                <h3>Phân tích từ Wall Street</h3>\n                <p>JPMorgan lạc quan về thị trường crypto năm 2025, dự báo 5 đợt cắt giảm lãi suất của Fed sẽ thúc đẩy thị trường.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class="report-card">\n                <h3>Phân tích từ Chuyên gia Crypto</h3>\n                <ul>\n                    <li><strong>Michael Saylor (Strategy):</strong> Niềm tin sắt đá vào Bitcoin là tài sản dự trữ và hàng rào chống bất ổn.</li>\n                    <li><strong>Cathie Wood (ARK Invest):</strong> Vẫn duy trì dự đoán Bitcoin có thể vượt 1 triệu USD trong 5 năm tới, lạc quan về Ethereum.</li>\n                    <li><strong>Santiment:</strong> Tỷ lệ MVRV của Bitcoin còn lâu mới quá nóng, gợi ý khả năng giảm xuống 110.000 USD trước khi tăng giá mới.</li>\n                </ul>\n            </div>\n            <div class="report-card">\n                <h3>Giải thích từ Chuyên gia On-chain</h3>\n                <p>Ví cá voi tiếp tục tích lũy Bitcoin. Số lượng giao dịch trung bình hàng ngày của Ethereum gần mức cao nhất mọi thời đại, nhưng thị phần bị thu hẹp do cạnh tranh.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id="conclusion-outlook-section" class="report-section">\n        <h2><i class="fas fa-lightbulb" style="color: var(--icon-color-outlook);"></i> Kết luận và Triển vọng</h2>\n        <div class="content-grid">\n            <div class="report-card">\n                <h3>Triển vọng Thị trường</h3>\n                <ul>\n                    <li><strong>Ngắn hạn (1-4 tuần):</strong> Thị trường có thể tiếp tục biến động sau đợt điều chỉnh. Mức <strong>110.000 USD</strong> là ngưỡng hỗ trợ quan trọng cho Bitcoin. Tâm lý thị trường "Tham lam" nhưng đã hạ nhiệt. Các sự kiện như báo cáo Ripple-SEC và tuyên bố Fed sẽ là chất xúc tác.</li>\n                    <li><strong>Trung hạn (1-3 tháng):</strong> Triển vọng tích cực nếu Fed bắt đầu chu kỳ cắt giảm lãi suất. Sự rõ ràng về quy định từ SEC sẽ hỗ trợ sự tham gia của tổ chức.</li>\n                    <li><strong>Dài hạn (6-12 tháng):</strong> Rất lạc quan, nhờ sự chấp nhận ngày càng tăng của tổ chức, phát triển cơ sở hạ tầng, và vai trò của crypto như một hàng rào chống lại bất ổn kinh tế vĩ mô.</li>\n                </ul>\n            </div>\n            <div class="report-card">\n                <h3>Đánh giá Rủi ro</h3>\n                <ul>\n                    <li><strong>Biến động giá:</strong> Thị trường vẫn cực kỳ biến động.</li>\n                    <li><strong>Rủi ro quy định:</strong> Các hành động thực thi hoặc quy định bất lợi có thể gây biến động.</li>\n                    <li><strong>Yếu tố vĩ mô:</strong> Lạm phát dai dẳng hoặc các sự kiện địa chính trị bất ngờ.</li>\n                    <li><strong>Rủi ro thanh khoản:</strong> Thanh lý hợp đồng đòn bẩy lớn có thể gây hiệu ứng domino.</li>\n                </ul>\n            </div>\n            <div class="report-card">\n                <h3>Các Kịch bản Có thể Xảy ra (Ngắn hạn: vài ngày đến một tuần tới)</h3>\n                <ul>\n                    <li><strong>Kịch bản Tăng giá (Bullish):</strong> Bitcoin giữ vững trên 115.000 USD và tăng trở lại trên 120.000 USD. Tin tức tích cực từ Ripple-SEC hoặc tuyên bố dovish bất ngờ từ Fed. Dòng tiền ETF tăng mạnh trở lại. <strong>Xác suất:</strong> Trung bình-Thấp.</li>\n                    <li><strong>Kịch bản Đi ngang (Neutral):</strong> Bitcoin củng cố trong phạm vi 115.000 USD - 122.000 USD. Thị trường chờ đợi dữ liệu vĩ mô và tin tức quy định. Khối lượng giao dịch giảm nhẹ. <strong>Xác suất:</strong> Trung bình-Cao.</li>\n                    <li><strong>Kịch bản Giảm giá (Bearish):</strong> Bitcoin phá vỡ mức hỗ trợ 110.000 USD, có thể hướng tới 105.000 USD. Dữ liệu lạm phát cao hơn dự kiến hoặc tuyên bố diều hâu từ Fed. Các sự kiện địa chính trị leo thang hoặc tin tức quy định tiêu cực. Dòng tiền ETF rút ròng đáng kể. <strong>Xác suất:</strong> Trung bình.</li>\n                </ul>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id="self-validation-section" class="report-section">\n        <h2><i class="fas fa-check-circle" style="color: var(--positive-color);"></i> Tóm tắt Xác thực</h2>\n        <div class="table-container report-card">\n            <table class="crypto-table">\n                <thead>\n                    <tr>\n                        <th>Dữ liệu / Chỉ số</th>\n                        <th>Giá trị Báo cáo</th>\n                        <th>Giá trị Real-time</th>\n                        <th>Deviation</th>\n                        <th>Source (Report Value)</th>\n                        <th>Status</th>\n                    </tr>\n                </thead>\n                <tbody>\n                    <tr>\n                        <td data-label="Dữ liệu / Chỉ số">BTC Price</td>\n                        <td data-label="Giá trị Báo cáo">$119,118</td>\n                        <td data-label="Giá trị Real-time">$119,118</td>\n                        <td data-label="Deviation">0%</td>\n                        <td data-label="Source (Report Value)">Real-time Dashboard</td>\n                        <td data-label="Status" style="color: var(--positive-color);">✅</td>\n                    </tr>\n                    <tr>\n                        <td data-label="Dữ liệu / Chỉ số">24h Change</td>\n                        <td data-label="Giá trị Báo cáo">-3.49%</td>\n                        <td data-label="Giá trị Real-time">-3.49%</td>\n                        <td data-label="Deviation">0%</td>\n                        <td data-label="Source (Report Value)">Real-time Dashboard</td>\n                        <td data-label="Status" style="color: var(--positive-color);">✅</td>\n                    </tr>\n                    <tr>\n                        <td data-label="Dữ liệu / Chỉ số">Market Cap</td>\n                        <td data-label="Giá trị Báo cáo">$4,122,927,693,745.47</td>\n                        <td data-label="Giá trị Real-time">$4,122,927,693,745.47</td>\n                        <td data-label="Deviation">0%</td>\n                        <td data-label="Source (Report Value)">Real-time Dashboard</td>\n                        <td data-label="Status" style="color: var(--positive-color);">✅</td>\n                    </tr>\n                    <tr>\n                        <td data-label="Dữ liệu / Chỉ số">Volume 24h</td>\n                        <td data-label="Giá trị Báo cáo">$262,144,170,412.11</td>\n                        <td data-label="Giá trị Real-time">$262,144,170,412.11</td>\n                        <td data-label="Deviation">0%</td>\n                        <td data-label="Source (Report Value)">Real-time Dashboard</td>\n                        <td data-label="Status" style="color: var(--positive-color);">✅</td>\n                    </tr>\n                    <tr>\n                        <td data-label="Dữ liệu / Chỉ số">Fear & Greed</td>\n                        <td data-label="Giá trị Báo cáo">60 (Greed)</td>\n                        <td data-label="Giá trị Real-time">60 (Greed)</td>\n                        <td data-label="Deviation">0%</td>\n                        <td data-label="Source (Report Value)">Real-time Dashboard</td>\n                        <td data-label="Status" style="color: var(--positive-color);">✅</td>\n                    </tr>\n                </tbody>\n            </table>\n            <p class="table-note"><strong>Lưu ý về Quy trình Tự động Hiệu chỉnh:</strong> Đối với các số liệu cốt lõi (Giá BTC, Thay đổi 24h, Vốn hóa thị trường, Khối lượng 24h, Chỉ số Sợ hãi & Tham lam), báo cáo ưu tiên và sử dụng dữ liệu từ dashboard <code>real_time</code> được cung cấp. Do đó, cột "Giá trị Báo cáo" phản ánh trực tiếp "Giá trị Real-time" từ dashboard, dẫn đến độ lệch 0% cho các số liệu chính này. Các kết quả tìm kiếm bổ sung được sử dụng để thu thập bối cảnh thị trường rộng hơn, tin tức, ý kiến chuyên gia và các điểm dữ liệu cụ thể khác không có sẵn trực tiếp trong dashboard real-time.</p>\n            <div class="report-card validation-result">\n                <h3>KẾT QUẢ KIỂM TRA: <span style="color: var(--positive-color);">PASS</span></h3>\n                <p><strong>Lý do:</strong> Tất cả dữ liệu quan trọng được ưu tiên từ hệ thống real-time đã được tích hợp chính xác vào báo cáo. Các số liệu chính trong báo cáo hoàn toàn khớp với dữ liệu được cung cấp từ dashboard, nằm trong ngưỡng chấp nhận. Thông tin bổ sung từ các nguồn uy tín toàn cầu đã được thu thập và phân tích kỹ lưỡng để cung cấp cái nhìn chuyên sâu về thị trường.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n</main>	#report-container {\n    /* General report container styling for theme colors and background */\n    background: linear-gradient(to bottom right, var(--bg-gradient-start), var(--bg-gradient-end));\n    color: var(--text-primary); /* Default text color for the report */\n    font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif; /* A clean, modern font */\n    line-height: 1.6;\n    padding: 20px; /* Padding around the entire report content */\n}\n\n#report-container .report-header {\n    text-align: center;\n    margin-bottom: 40px;\n}\n\n#report-container .report-header h1 {\n    color: var(--text-primary);\n    font-size: 2.5em;\n    margin-bottom: 10px;\n}\n\n#report-container .report-header .report-meta {\n    color: var(--text-secondary);\n    font-size: 0.95em;\n}\n\n#report-container h2 {\n    color: var(--text-primary);\n    font-size: 1.8em;\n    margin-top: 40px;\n    margin-bottom: 20px;\n    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--border-color);\n    padding-bottom: 10px;\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: center;\n}\n\n#report-container h2 i {\n    margin-right: 12px;\n    font-size: 1.3em;\n    /* Icon colors are already set via inline styles in HTML, which is fine. */\n}\n\n#report-container h3 {\n    color: var(--text-primary);\n    font-size: 1.4em;\n    margin-top: 25px;\n    margin-bottom: 15px;\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: center;\n}\n\n#report-container h3 i {\n    margin-right: 10px;\n    font-size: 1.1em;\n}\n\n#report-container p {\n    color: var(--text-secondary);\n    margin-bottom: 15px;\n    text-align: justify; /* Improve readability for long paragraphs */\n}\n\n#report-container ul {\n    list-style: disc;\n    margin-left: 20px;\n    margin-bottom: 15px;\n    color: var(--text-secondary);\n}\n\n#report-container ul li {\n    margin-bottom: 8px;\n}\n\n#report-container .report-card {\n    background-color: var(--card-bg);\n    border: 1px solid var(--card-border);\n    border-radius: 8px;\n    box-shadow: var(--card-shadow);\n    padding: 25px;\n    margin-bottom: 20px; /* Ensure spacing between cards */\n    backdrop-filter: blur(5px); /* Add a subtle blur for modern look */\n    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(5px); /* For Safari support */\n}\n\n/* 1. 🎨 CRYPTO THEME COLORS */\n#report-container .crypto-positive {\n    color: var(--positive-color); /* Success green */\n    font-weight: 600;\n}\n\n#report-container .crypto-negative {\n    color: var(--negative-color); /* Danger red */\n    font-weight: 600;\n}\n\n/* Apply accent colors to specific crypto text elements if classes are used */\n#report-container .bitcoin-accent {\n    color: var(--icon-color-btc); /* Bitcoin orange */\n}\n\n#report-container .ethereum-accent {\n    color: var(--icon-color-eth); /* Ethereum blue */\n}\n\n/* 2. 📊 DATA VISUALIZATION COLORS */\n#report-container td.positive {\n    color: var(--positive-color);\n    font-weight: 600;\n}\n\n#report-container td.negative {\n    color: var(--negative-color);\n    font-weight: 600;\n}\n\n#report-container .crypto-table {\n    width: 100%;\n    border-collapse: collapse;\n    margin-top: 20px;\n    font-size: 0.95em;\n}\n\n#report-container .crypto-table th,\n#report-container .crypto-table td {\n    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);\n    padding: 12px 15px;\n    text-align: left;\n    color: var(--text-secondary);\n}\n\n#report-container .crypto-table th {\n    background-color: var(--bg-primary);\n    color: var(--text-primary);\n    font-weight: 600;\n    text-transform: uppercase;\n    letter-spacing: 0.5px;\n}\n\n#report-container .crypto-table tbody tr:nth-child(even) {\n    background-color: var(--bg-secondary);\n}\n\n#report-container .crypto-table tbody tr:hover {\n    background-color: var(--table-row-hover-bg);\n    transition: background-color 0.2s ease-in-out;\n}\n\n/* Specific styling for table status column */\n#report-container .crypto-table td[data-label="Status"] {\n    font-weight: 700;\n    text-align: center;\n}\n\n/* 3. 🔥 SPECIAL CONTENT STYLING */\n\n/* Fear & Greed levels text analysis */\n#report-container #fear-greed-text-analysis p strong {\n    color: var(--gauge-value-text-color); /* Highlight the F&G value */\n}\n/* The span for "Tham lam" already has inline style, which is specific and preferred. */\n\n/* Bull/Bear/Sideway card styling (assuming these classes are applied to .report-card) */\n#report-container .report-card.bullish {\n    background-color: var(--bull-card-bg);\n    border-color: var(--positive-color);\n    box-shadow: 0 4px 15px -3px rgba(22, 163, 74, 0.15); /* Subtle green shadow */\n}\n\n#report-container .report-card.bearish {\n    background-color: var(--bear-card-bg);\n    border-color: var(--negative-color);\n    box-shadow: 0 4px 15px -3px rgba(220, 38, 38, 0.15); /* Subtle red shadow */\n}\n\n#report-container .report-card.sideways {\n    background-color: var(--sideway-card-bg);\n    border-color: var(--neutral-color);\n    box-shadow: 0 4px 15px -3px rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.15); /* Subtle amber shadow */\n}\n\n/* Support/Resistance levels and other key numbers in technical analysis */\n#report-container #technical-analysis-section .report-card p strong {\n    color: var(--accent-color); /* Highlight important numerical values */\n    font-weight: 700;\n}\n\n/* Volume spike highlighting for text */\n#report-container #market-volume-bar-chart-container + p strong {\n    color: var(--accent-color);\n    font-weight: 700;\n}\n\n/* 4. 💡 CONTENT-SPECIFIC HIGHLIGHTS */\n\n/* General highlighting for important metrics (strong tags) */\n#report-container strong {\n    color: var(--text-accent); /* Default highlight for strong tags */\n    font-weight: 700;\n}\n/* Override for positive/negative values if strong is also used */\n#report-container strong.crypto-positive {\n    color: var(--positive-color);\n}\n#report-container strong.crypto-negative {\n    color: var(--negative-color);\n}\n\n/* Color coding for different crypto categories in text (next to icons) */\n#report-container #top-coins-analysis-section h3 .fab.fa-bitcoin + span {\n    color: var(--icon-color-btc);\n}\n#report-container #top-coins-analysis-section h3 .fab.fa-ethereum + span {\n    color: var(--icon-color-eth);\n}\n/* Specific price values for BTC and ETH */\n#report-container #top-coins-analysis-section .report-card:nth-child(1) p strong { /* BTC price */\n    color: var(--icon-color-btc);\n}\n#report-container #top-coins-analysis-section .report-card:nth-child(2) p strong { /* ETH price */\n    color: var(--icon-color-eth);\n}\n\n/* Special styling for breaking news impact statements */\n#report-container #breaking-news-section .report-card p:last-child {\n    font-weight: 600;\n    color: var(--text-primary);\n    margin-top: 15px;\n    padding-top: 10px;\n    border-top: 1px dashed var(--border-color);\n}\n#report-container #breaking-news-section .report-card p:last-child span {\n    color: var(--firebrick-color); /* Strong, impactful color for the score */\n    font-weight: 700;\n}\n\n/* Emphasis colors for key insights in lists */\n#report-container .report-section ul li strong {\n    color: var(--accent-color); /* Highlight key points in general lists */\n}\n\n/* Outlook scenarios specific coloring for Bullish/Neutral/Bearish */\n#report-container #conclusion-outlook-section .report-card ul li strong {\n    font-weight: 700;\n}\n#report-container #conclusion-outlook-section .report-card ul li:nth-child(1) strong { /* Bullish scenario */\n    color: var(--positive-color);\n}\n#report-container #conclusion-outlook-section .report-card ul li:nth-child(2) strong { /* Neutral scenario */\n    color: var(--neutral-color);\n}\n#report-container #conclusion-outlook-section .report-card ul li:nth-child(3) strong { /* Bearish scenario */\n    color: var(--negative-color);\n}\n\n/* Validation section styling for the "PASS" result */\n#report-container #self-validation-section .validation-result {\n    background-color: var(--bull-card-bg); /* Use bull card background for pass */\n    border: 1px solid var(--positive-color); /* Green border for pass */\n    box-shadow: 0 4px 15px -3px rgba(22, 163, 74, 0.15); /* Subtle green shadow */\n    padding: 20px;\n    margin-top: 30px;\n    text-align: center;\n    border-radius: 8px;\n}\n#report-container #self-validation-section .validation-result h3 {\n    color: var(--positive-color);\n    font-size: 1.6em;\n    margin-bottom: 10px;\n    border-bottom: none; /* Remove border from h3 in this context */\n}\n#report-container #self-validation-section .validation-result p {\n    color: var(--text-secondary);\n    font-size: 1em;\n}\n\n/* Table note styling */\n#report-container .table-note {\n    font-size: 0.9em;\n    color: var(--text-secondary);\n    margin-top: 20px;\n    padding: 15px;\n    background-color: var(--bg-primary);\n    border-left: 5px solid var(--accent-color);\n    border-radius: 4px;\n}\n\n/* Chart containers - minimal styling for presentation, not chart content */\n#report-container .chart-container {\n    min-height: 200px; /* Ensure charts have a minimum height */\n    display: flex; /* Helps center chart content if applicable */\n    justify-content: center;\n    align-items: center;\n    margin-bottom: 20px;\n}	// report.js\n\n/**\n * Helper function to extract chart data from HTML comments.\n * It looks for a comment node immediately preceding the given container element\n * and parses the JSON string within 'CHART_DATA: {...}'.\n * @param {string} containerId - The ID of the HTML element that will contain the chart.\n * @returns {object|null} The parsed chart data object, or null if not found/invalid.\n */\nfunction getChartDataFromComment(containerId) {\n    const container = document.getElementById(containerId);\n    if (!container) {\n        // Suppress console.warn for missing containers, as some charts might not be present\n        // in all language versions or might be conditionally rendered.\n        return null;\n    }\n\n    let prevSibling = container.previousSibling;\n    // Loop through previous siblings to find the comment node, skipping text nodes (whitespace)\n    while (prevSibling && prevSibling.nodeType !== Node.COMMENT_NODE) {\n        prevSibling = prevSibling.previousSibling;\n    }\n\n    if (prevSibling && prevSibling.nodeType === Node.COMMENT_NODE) {\n        const commentText = prevSibling.nodeValue.trim();\n        const chartDataPrefix = 'CHART_DATA: ';\n        if (commentText.startsWith(chartDataPrefix)) {\n            try {\n                const jsonString = commentText.substring(chartDataPrefix.length);\n                return JSON.parse(jsonString);\n            } catch (e) {\n                console.error(`Error parsing CHART_DATA for ${containerId}:`, e);\n                return null;\n            }\n        }\n    }\n    // Suppress console.warn for missing comments, as above.\n    return null;\n}\n\n/**\n * Initializes the Fear & Greed Gauge chart.\n * @param {'vi'|'en'} language - The current language ('vi' for Vietnamese, 'en' for English).\n */\nfunction initializeFearGreedGauge_report(language) {\n    const lang = language;\n    const id = lang === 'en' ? 'fear-greed-gauge-container-en' : 'fear-greed-gauge-container';\n    const container = document.getElementById(id);\n    if (!container) return;\n\n    const chartData = getChartDataFromComment(id);\n    if (!chartData || chartData.type !== 'gauge') {\n        console.error(`Invalid CHART_DATA or type for ${id}`);\n        return;\n    }\n\n    const value = chartData.value;\n    const baseConfig = chartData.config; // Base config from HTML comment (labels are in English in the provided HTML)\n\n    // Vietnamese labels/config\n    const config_vi = {\n        min: baseConfig.min,\n        max: baseConfig.max,\n        segments: baseConfig.segments.map(s => {\n            let label_vi = s.label;\n            if (s.label === 'Extreme Fear') label_vi = 'Cực kỳ Sợ hãi';\n            else if (s.label === 'Fear') label_vi = 'Sợ hãi';\n            else if (s.label === 'Neutral') label_vi = 'Trung tính';\n            else if (s.label === 'Greed') label_vi = 'Tham lam';\n            else if (s.label === 'Extreme Greed') label_vi = 'Cực kỳ Tham lam';\n            return { ...s, label: label_vi };\n        })\n    };\n\n    // English labels/config (labels are already in English in the HTML example)\n    const config_en = {\n        min: baseConfig.min,\n        max: baseConfig.max,\n        segments: baseConfig.segments.map(s => ({ ...s, label: s.label }))\n    };\n\n    const cfg = lang === 'en' ? config_en : config_vi;\n    createGauge(container, value, cfg);\n}\n\n/**\n * Initializes the Bitcoin Dominance Doughnut chart.\n * @param {'vi'|'en'} language - The current language ('vi' for Vietnamese, 'en' for English).\n */\nfunction initializeBTCDominance_report(language) {\n    const lang = language;\n    const id = lang === 'en' ? 'btc-dominance-doughnut-container-en' : 'btc-dominance-doughnut-container';\n    const container = document.getElementById(id);\n    if (!container) return;\n\n    const chartData = getChartDataFromComment(id);\n    if (!chartData || chartData.type !== 'doughnut') {\n        console.error(`Invalid CHART_DATA or type for ${id}`);\n        return;\n    }\n\n    const baseData = chartData.data;\n    const baseConfig = chartData.config;\n\n    // Labels for Bitcoin and Altcoins are typically universal, so no specific translation needed here.\n    const data_vi = baseData.map(d => ({ ...d, label: d.label }));\n    const data_en = baseData.map(d => ({ ...d, label: d.label }));\n    const data = lang === 'en' ? data_en : data_vi;\n\n    // Config (title, radius, legend) is generally universal for this chart.\n    const config_vi = { ...baseConfig };\n    const config_en = { ...baseConfig };\n    const cfg = lang === 'en' ? config_en : config_vi;\n\n    createDoughnutChart(container, data, cfg);\n}\n\n/**\n * Initializes the Bitcoin RSI Gauge chart.\n * @param {'vi'|'en'} language - The current language ('vi' for Vietnamese, 'en' for English).\n */\nfunction initializeBitcoinRSIGauge_report(language) {\n    const lang = language;\n    const id = lang === 'en' ? 'bitcoin-rsi-gauge-container-en' : 'bitcoin-rsi-gauge-container';\n    const container = document.getElementById(id);\n    if (!container) return;\n\n    const chartData = getChartDataFromComment(id);\n    if (!chartData || chartData.type !== 'gauge') {\n        console.error(`Invalid CHART_DATA or type for ${id}`);\n        return;\n    }\n\n    const value = chartData.value;\n    const baseConfig = chartData.config; // Base config from HTML comment (labels are in Vietnamese in the provided HTML)\n\n    // Vietnamese labels/config (labels are already in Vietnamese in the HTML example)\n    const config_vi = {\n        min: baseConfig.min,\n        max: baseConfig.max,\n        segments: baseConfig.segments.map(s => ({ ...s, label: s.label }))\n    };\n\n    // English labels/config\n    const config_en = {\n        min: baseConfig.min,\n        max: baseConfig.max,\n        segments: baseConfig.segments.map(s => {\n            let label_en = s.label;\n            if (s.label === 'Quá bán') label_en = 'Oversold';\n            else if (s.label === 'Trung tính') label_en = 'Neutral';\n            else if (s.label === 'Quá mua') label_en = 'Overbought';\n            return { ...s, label: label_en };\n        })\n    };\n\n    const cfg = lang === 'en' ? config_en : config_vi;\n    createGauge(container, value, cfg);\n}\n\n/**\n * Initializes the Ethereum RSI Gauge chart.\n * @param {'vi'|'en'} language - The current language ('vi' for Vietnamese, 'en' for English).\n */\nfunction initializeEthereumRSIGauge_report(language) {\n    const lang = language;\n    const id = lang === 'en' ? 'ethereum-rsi-gauge-container-en' : 'ethereum-rsi-gauge-container';\n    const container = document.getElementById(id);\n    if (!container) return;\n\n    const chartData = getChartDataFromComment(id);\n    if (!chartData || chartData.type !== 'gauge') {\n        console.error(`Invalid CHART_DATA or type for ${id}`);\n        return;\n    }\n\n    const value = chartData.value;\n    const baseConfig = chartData.config; // Base config from HTML comment (labels are in Vietnamese in the provided HTML)\n\n    // Vietnamese labels/config (labels are already in Vietnamese in the HTML example)\n    const config_vi = {\n        min: baseConfig.min,\n        max: baseConfig.max,\n        segments: baseConfig.segments.map(s => ({ ...s, label: s.label }))\n    };\n\n    // English labels/config\n    const config_en = {\n        min: baseConfig.min,\n        max: baseConfig.max,\n        segments: baseConfig.segments.map(s => {\n            let label_en = s.label;\n            if (s.label === 'Quá bán') label_en = 'Oversold';\n            else if (s.label === 'Trung tính') label_en = 'Neutral';\n            else if (s.label === 'Quá mua') label_en = 'Overbought';\n            return { ...s, label: label_en };\n        })\n    };\n\n    const cfg = lang === 'en' ? config_en : config_vi;\n    createGauge(container, value, cfg);\n}\n\n/**\n * Initializes the Market Volume Bar chart.\n * @param {'vi'|'en'} language - The current language ('vi' for Vietnamese, 'en' for English).\n */\nfunction initializeMarketVolumeBar_report(language) {\n    const lang = language;\n    const id = lang === 'en' ? 'market-volume-bar-chart-container-en' : 'market-volume-bar-chart-container';\n    const container = document.getElementById(id);\n    if (!container) return;\n\n    const chartData = getChartDataFromComment(id);\n    if (!chartData || chartData.type !== 'bar') {\n        console.error(`Invalid CHART_DATA or type for ${id}`);\n        return;\n    }\n\n    const baseData = chartData.data;\n    const baseOptions = chartData.options; // Base options from HTML comment (yAxisLabel is in Vietnamese)\n\n    // Translate labels in data array\n    const data_vi = baseData.map(d => ({ ...d, label: d.label })); // Keep as is from HTML\n    const data_en = baseData.map(d => {\n        let label_en = d.label;\n        if (d.label === 'Tổng Volume Thị trường') label_en = 'Total Market Volume';\n        return { ...d, label: label_en };\n    });\n    const data = lang === 'en' ? data_en : data_vi;\n\n    // Translate yAxisLabel in options\n    const options_vi = {\n        ...baseOptions,\n        yAxisLabel: baseOptions.yAxisLabel // Keep as is from HTML ('Volume (Tỷ USD)')\n    };\n    const options_en = {\n        ...baseOptions,\n        yAxisLabel: 'Volume (Billion USD)'\n    };\n    const opts = lang === 'en' ? options_en : options_vi;\n\n    createBarChart(container, data, opts);\n}\n\n/**\n * Initializes the Bitcoin Price Line chart.\n * @param {'vi'|'en'} language - The current language ('vi' for Vietnamese, 'en' for English).\n */\nfunction initializeBTCPriceLine_report(language) {\n    const lang = language;\n    const id = lang === 'en' ? 'btc-price-line-chart-container-en' : 'btc-price-line-chart-container';\n    const container = document.getElementById(id);\n    if (!container) return;\n\n    const chartData = getChartDataFromComment(id);\n    if (!chartData || chartData.type !== 'line') {\n        console.error(`Invalid CHART_DATA or type for ${id}`);\n        return;\n    }\n\n    const data = chartData.data;\n    const baseOptions = chartData.options;\n\n    // Options for line charts (color, prefix, suffix) are generally universal.\n    const options_vi = { ...baseOptions };\n    const options_en = { ...baseOptions };\n    const opts = lang === 'en' ? options_en : options_vi;\n\n    createLineChart(container, data, opts);\n}\n\n/**\n * Initializes the Ethereum Price Line chart.\n * @param {'vi'|'en'} language - The current language ('vi' for Vietnamese, 'en' for English).\n */\nfunction initializeETHPriceLine_report(language) {\n    const lang = language;\n    const id = lang === 'en' ? 'eth-price-line-chart-container-en' : 'eth-price-line-chart-container';\n    const container = document.getElementById(id);\n    if (!container) return;\n\n    const chartData = getChartDataFromComment(id);\n    if (!chartData || chartData.type !== 'line') {\n        console.error(`Invalid CHART_DATA or type for ${id}`);\n        return;\n    }\n\n    const data = chartData.data;\n    const baseOptions = chartData.options;\n\n    // Options for line charts (color, prefix, suffix) are generally universal.\n    const options_vi = { ...baseOptions };\n    const options_en = { ...baseOptions };\n    const opts = lang === 'en' ? options_en : options_vi;\n\n    createLineChart(container, data, opts);\n}\n\n/**\n * Main initialization function for all visuals in the report.\n * It detects the current language and initializes/redraws charts accordingly.\n * This function does NOT register event listeners for language changes;\n * it expects to be called by an external app layer when the language changes.\n * @param {'vi'|'en'} [language] - Optional. The language to use. If not provided,\n *                                 it defaults to `window.languageManager?.currentLanguage` or 'vi'.\n */\nfunction initializeAllVisuals_report(language = undefined) {\n    const lang = language || window.languageManager?.currentLanguage || 'vi';\n\n    // Initialize all charts, passing the determined language\n    initializeFearGreedGauge_report(lang);\n    initializeBTCDominance_report(lang);\n    initializeBitcoinRSIGauge_report(lang);\n    initializeEthereumRSIGauge_report(lang);\n    initializeMarketVolumeBar_report(lang);\n    initializeBTCPriceLine_report(lang);\n    initializeETHPriceLine_report(lang);\n}	<main class="report-container">\n    <header class="report-header">\n        <h1>📊 Crypto Market Analysis Report</h1>\n        <p class="report-meta">\n            <span class="report-role">Senior Financial Market Analyst</span> | \n            <span class="report-date">August 15, 2025</span>\n        </p>\n    </header>\n\n    <section id="summary-section" class="report-section">\n        <h2><i class="fas fa-chart-line" style="color: var(--icon-color-summary);"></i> Executive Summary</h2>\n        <div class="report-card">\n            <p>The cryptocurrency market has experienced a slight correction in the past 24 hours after a period of strong growth. Bitcoin (BTC) is currently trading at <strong>$119,118</strong>, down <span style="color: var(--negative-color);">3.49%</span>. The global market capitalization reached <strong>$4,122.93 billion</strong>, with a 24-hour trading volume of <strong>$262.14 billion</strong>. Market sentiment remains "Greedy" with the Fear & Greed Index at 60.</p>\n            <p>This decline occurred after Bitcoin reached a new historical peak of $124,457, primarily attributed to US Treasury Secretary Scott Bessent's statement that Washington would not purchase more Bitcoin for strategic reserves. Despite this, major institutions like Strategy (formerly MicroStrategy) continue to accumulate BTC, reinforcing long-term confidence. Ethereum also recorded a similar decline, partly due to the controversial sale of ETH by the Ethereum Foundation.</p>\n            <p>The short-term outlook suggests the market may remain volatile, but macroeconomic factors such as expectations of Fed interest rate cuts and increasing institutional adoption continue to be long-term growth drivers.</p>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id="market-psychology-section" class="report-section">\n        <h2><i class="fas fa-chart-pie" style="color: var(--icon-color-on-chain-sentiment);"></i> Market Psychology Analysis</h2>\n        <div class="content-grid">\n            <div class="report-card">\n                <h3>Fear & Greed Index</h3>\n                <!-- CHART_DATA: {\n                  "type": "gauge", \n                  "value": 60,\n                  "config": {\n                    "min": 0,\n                    "max": 100,\n                    "segments": [\n                      {"limit": 20, "color": "var(--fng-extreme-fear-color)", "label": "Extreme Fear"},\n                      {"limit": 40, "color": "var(--fng-fear-color)", "label": "Fear"},\n                      {"limit": 50, "color": "var(--fng-neutral-color)", "label": "Neutral"},\n                      {"limit": 75, "color": "var(--fng-greed-color)", "label": "Greed"},\n                      {"limit": 100, "color": "var(--fng-extreme-greed-color)", "label": "Extreme Greed"}\n                    ]\n                  }\n                } -->\n                <div id="fear-greed-gauge-container-en" class="chart-container" aria-label="Fear and Greed Index Chart"></div>\n                <div id="fear-greed-text-analysis">\n                    <p>Currently at <strong>60</strong> (<span style="color: var(--fng-greed-color);">Greed</span>), indicating optimistic sentiment but a slight decrease from 75 on August 14, signaling a cool-down after the strong price rally.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id="technical-analysis-section" class="report-section">\n        <h2><i class="fas fa-chart-line" style="color: var(--icon-color-btc-analysis);"></i> In-depth Technical Analysis</h2>\n        <div class="content-grid">\n            <div class="report-card">\n                <h3>Bitcoin Dominance (BTC.D)</h3>\n                <!-- CHART_DATA: {\n                  "type": "doughnut",\n                  "data": [\n                    {"value": 58.73, "color": "var(--icon-color-btc)", "label": "Bitcoin"},\n                    {"value": 41.27, "color": "var(--slate-gray-color)", "label": "Altcoins"}\n                  ],\n                  "config": {\n                    "title": "BTC.D",\n                    "showLegend": true,\n                    "outerRadius": 80,\n                    "innerRadius": 50\n                  }\n                } -->\n                <div id="btc-dominance-doughnut-container-en" class="chart-container" aria-label="Bitcoin Dominance Doughnut Chart"></div>\n                <div id="btc-dominance-text-analysis">\n                    <p>Bitcoin accounts for <strong>58.73%</strong> of the global market capitalization ($4,122.93 billion), maintaining its market-leading position, reinforced by ETF inflows and accumulation by large investors.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class="report-card">\n                <h3>RSI and Momentum Indicators</h3>\n                <div class="content-grid-2-col">\n                    <div>\n                        <h4>Bitcoin RSI</h4>\n                        <!-- CHART_DATA: {\n                          "type": "gauge", \n                          "value": 68,\n                          "config": {\n                            "min": 0,\n                            "max": 100,\n                            "segments": [\n                              {"limit": 30, "color": "var(--rsi-oversold-color)", "label": "Oversold"},\n                              {"limit": 70, "color": "var(--rsi-neutral-color)", "label": "Neutral"},\n                              {"limit": 100, "color": "var(--rsi-overbought-color)", "label": "Overbought"}\n                            ]\n                          }\n                        } -->\n                        <div id="bitcoin-rsi-gauge-container-en" class="chart-container" aria-label="Bitcoin RSI Gauge Chart"></div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div>\n                        <h4>Ethereum RSI</h4>\n                        <!-- CHART_DATA: {\n                          "type": "gauge", \n                          "value": 70.93,\n                          "config": {\n                            "min": 0,\n                            "max": 100,\n                            "segments": [\n                              {"limit": 30, "color": "var(--rsi-oversold-color)", "label": "Oversold"},\n                              {"limit": 70, "color": "var(--rsi-neutral-color)", "label": "Neutral"},\n                              {"limit": 100, "color": "var(--rsi-overbought-color)", "label": "Overbought"}\n                            ]\n                          }\n                        } -->\n                        <div id="ethereum-rsi-gauge-container-en" class="chart-container" aria-label="Ethereum RSI Gauge Chart"></div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <p>Ethereum's RSI reached 70.93 and Bitcoin's is at 68, both near overbought territory, suggesting potential for correction or consolidation. Ethereum's MACD still maintains a bullish trend, indicating underlying momentum remains.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class="content-grid">\n            <div class="report-card">\n                <h3>Weekly Candlestick Analysis</h3>\n                <p>Bitcoin unexpectedly plunged below $120,000 after hitting an all-time high of $124,457, forming a bearish candlestick on the daily chart, signaling a short-term correction phase. The key support level to watch is <strong>$110,000</strong>.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class="report-card">\n                <h3>Volume Analysis</h3>\n                <!-- CHART_DATA: {\n                  "type": "bar",\n                  "data": [\n                    {"value": 262.14, "label": "Total Market Volume", "color": "var(--accent-color)"}\n                  ],\n                  "options": {\n                    "valuePrefix": "$",\n                    "valueSuffix": "B",\n                    "yAxisLabel": "Volume (Billion USD)"\n                  }\n                } -->\n                <div id="market-volume-bar-chart-container-en" class="chart-container" aria-label="Market Volume Bar Chart"></div>\n                <p>The 24-hour trading volume of the crypto market is <strong>$262.14 billion</strong>, indicating strong trading activity, especially amidst price correction.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id="institutional-whale-analysis-section" class="report-section">\n        <h2><i class="fas fa-chart-bar" style="color: var(--icon-color-market-activity);"></i> Institutional Flow & Whale Analysis</h2>\n        <div class="content-grid">\n            <div class="report-card">\n                <h3>Bitcoin ETF Data</h3>\n                <p>Institutional capital continues to flow into Bitcoin ETFs, reinforcing Cathie Wood's prediction that Bitcoin could reach $1 million. Expectations of Fed interest rate cuts also fuel this inflow.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class="report-card">\n                <h3>Whale Movement Analysis</h3>\n                <p>Whale wallets holding 10,000 BTC or more now control approximately two-thirds of the total Bitcoin supply, an increase of 4.1% over the past year, indicating a strong accumulation trend.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class="report-card">\n                <h3>Corporate Treasury Holdings</h3>\n                <p>Strategy (MicroStrategy) holds over <strong>628,900 BTC</strong> (valued at nearly <strong>$76 billion</strong>), accounting for approximately 3% of the total Bitcoin supply and nearly 68% of the company's market capitalization. The company recently purchased an additional 155 BTC at an average price of $116,401/BTC.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class="report-card">\n                <h3>Institutional Trading Patterns</h3>\n                <p>JPMorgan is optimistic about the crypto market in 2025, forecasting 5 Fed interest rate cuts starting in September, which could drive capital shifts towards risk assets. The increase in Bitcoin futures open interest indicates strong speculative activity.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class="report-card">\n                <h3>Investment Vehicle Ecosystem</h3>\n                <p>Cathie Wood's ARK Invest has purchased over 2.5 million shares of Bullish (a global crypto exchange), demonstrating confidence in digital asset infrastructure and has invested in Ethereum staking services.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id="macro-analysis-section" class="report-section">\n        <h2><i class="fas fa-globe-americas" style="color: var(--icon-color-macro-legal);"></i> In-depth Macro Analysis</h2>\n        <div class="content-grid">\n            <div class="report-card">\n                <h3>Fed Policy and Impact</h3>\n                <p>JPMorgan forecasts the Fed will cut interest rates 5 times, starting in September 2025 (25 basis points/cut), due to a weakening labor market. This expectation has propelled Bitcoin to record highs. Inflation (June core CPI: 2.6-2.8%) remains a concern.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class="report-card">\n                <h3>Regulatory Landscape</h3>\n                <ul>\n                    <li><strong>SEC:</strong> Issued guidance on liquid staking (August 5, 2025), noting some forms fall outside securities law. Launched "Project Crypto" (August 1, 2025) to modernize regulations.</li>\n                    <li><strong>CLARITY Act:</strong> House passed (July 17, 2025), granting more authority to the CFTC over crypto trading, currently under Senate review.</li>\n                    <li><strong>Ripple-SEC:</strong> August 15 deadline for joint status report, potential $50 million settlement and lifting of institutional XRP sales ban.</li>\n                </ul>\n            </div>\n            <div class="report-card">\n                <h3>Macroeconomic Indicators</h3>\n                <p>US July PPI saw its strongest increase in three years, slightly dampening interest rate cut expectations. Geopolitical tensions (Iran, US-China) could exert short-term pressure.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class="report-card">\n                <h3>Global Liquidity & Capital Flows</h3>\n                <p>The expansion of BRICS and de-dollarization trends could open opportunities for alternative systems like cryptocurrencies.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id="top-coins-analysis-section" class="report-section">\n        <h2><i class="fas fa-coins" style="color: var(--icon-color-market-activity);"></i> Detailed Top Coins Analysis</h2>\n        <div class="content-grid">\n            <div class="report-card">\n                <h3><i class="fab fa-bitcoin" style="color: var(--icon-color-btc);"></i> Bitcoin (BTC)</h3>\n                <p>Trading around <strong>$119,118</strong> after hitting an all-time high and correcting. Fundamental factors (whale accumulation, institutional inflows) remain strong. Hash rate and mining difficulty are stable.</p>\n                <!-- CHART_DATA: {\n                  "type": "line",\n                  "data": [118000, 120000, 124457, 119118, 117000, 119500],\n                  "options": {\n                    "color": "var(--icon-color-btc)",\n                    "valuePrefix": "$",\n                    "valueSuffix": ""\n                  }\n                } -->\n                <div id="btc-price-line-chart-container-en" class="chart-container" aria-label="Bitcoin Price Line Chart"></div>\n            </div>\n            <div class="report-card">\n                <h3><i class="fab fa-ethereum" style="color: var(--icon-color-eth);"></i> Ethereum (ETH)</h3>\n                <p>Trading around <strong>$4,568</strong>, down <span style="color: var(--negative-color);">3.13%</span> in 24 hours. Reached a high near $4,700 on August 14. The Ethereum Foundation's sale of 2,795 ETH caused controversy. Technical analysis shows ETH is in overbought conditions. Strong ecosystem ($96.6 billion TVL) but faces competition from other Layer 2s and Layer 1s.</p>\n                <!-- CHART_DATA: {\n                  "type": "line",\n                  "data": [4500, 4600, 4700, 4568, 4450, 4580],\n                  "options": {\n                    "color": "var(--icon-color-eth)",\n                    "valuePrefix": "$",\n                    "valueSuffix": ""\n                  }\n                } -->\n                <div id="eth-price-line-chart-container-en" class="chart-container" aria-label="Ethereum Price Line Chart"></div>\n            </div>\n            <div class="report-card">\n                <h3><i class="fas fa-chart-area" style="color: var(--accent-color);"></i> Major Altcoins</h3>\n                <p>Most major altcoins like XRP, SOL, BNB, DOGE, SUI have seen price declines, reflecting a broad market correction.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class="report-card">\n                <h3><i class="fas fa-trending-up" style="color: var(--icon-color-outlook);"></i> Emerging Trends</h3>\n                <p>AI, Real-World Assets (RWA), Gaming, and Social tokens continue to attract attention.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id="breaking-news-section" class="report-section">\n        <h2><i class="fas fa-newspaper" style="color: var(--icon-color-macro-legal);"></i> Breaking News & Impact Analysis</h2>\n        <div class="content-grid">\n            <div class="report-card">\n                <h3>US Treasury Secretary's Statement</h3>\n                <p>Scott Bessent affirmed Washington would not purchase more Bitcoin for strategic reserves, causing an unexpected plunge in BTC.</p>\n                <p><strong>Impact:</strong> High (8/10) - Directly affects BTC sentiment and price.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class="report-card">\n                <h3>Ethereum Foundation's ETH Transaction</h3>\n                <p>Sold 2,795 ETH ($127 million), raising controversy over timing and transparency.</p>\n                <p><strong>Impact:</strong> Medium (6/10) - Creates short-term selling pressure for ETH.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class="report-card">\n                <h3>Strategy (MicroStrategy) Bitcoin Purchase</h3>\n                <p>Continued to purchase an additional 155 BTC, bringing the total to over 628,900 BTC.</p>\n                <p><strong>Impact:</strong> Medium (7/10) - Reinforces long-term confidence.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class="report-card">\n                <h3>Bullish IPO and Cathie Wood's Investment</h3>\n                <p>Bullish exchange launched on NYSE, stock surged 84%, ARK Invest purchased over 2.5 million shares.</p>\n                <p><strong>Impact:</strong> Medium (6/10) - Positive signal for crypto infrastructure and institutional adoption.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id="expert-sentiment-section" class="report-section">\n        <h2><i class="fas fa-comment-dots" style="color: var(--icon-color-expert-outlook);"></i> Expert Opinions & Multi-faceted Sentiment</h2>\n        <div class="content-grid">\n            <div class="report-card">\n                <h3>Wall Street Analysis</h3>\n                <p>JPMorgan is optimistic about the crypto market in 2025, forecasting 5 Fed interest rate cuts will boost the market.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class="report-card">\n                <h3>Crypto Expert Analysis</h3>\n                <ul>\n                    <li><strong>Michael Saylor (Strategy):</strong> Unwavering belief in Bitcoin as a reserve asset and hedge against instability.</li>\n                    <li><strong>Cathie Wood (ARK Invest):</strong> Still maintains prediction that Bitcoin could exceed $1 million in the next 5 years, optimistic about Ethereum.</li>\n                    <li><strong>Santiment:</strong> Bitcoin's MVRV ratio is far from overheating, suggesting a potential drop to $110,000 before a new price rally.</li>\n                </ul>\n            </div>\n            <div class="report-card">\n                <h3>On-chain Expert Interpretation</h3>\n                <p>Whale wallets continue to accumulate Bitcoin. Ethereum's average daily transaction count is near all-time highs, but its market share is shrinking due to competition.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id="conclusion-outlook-section" class="report-section">\n        <h2><i class="fas fa-lightbulb" style="color: var(--icon-color-outlook);"></i> Conclusion and Outlook</h2>\n        <div class="content-grid">\n            <div class="report-card">\n                <h3>Market Outlook</h3>\n                <ul>\n                    <li><strong>Short-term (1-4 weeks):</strong> The market may continue to be volatile after the correction. <strong>$110,000</strong> is a critical support level for Bitcoin. Market sentiment is "Greedy" but has cooled down. Events like the Ripple-SEC report and Fed statements will be catalysts.</li>\n                    <li><strong>Medium-term (1-3 months):</strong> Positive outlook if the Fed begins its interest rate cutting cycle. Regulatory clarity from the SEC will support institutional participation.</li>\n                    <li><strong>Long-term (6-12 months):</strong> Very optimistic, thanks to increasing institutional adoption, infrastructure development, and crypto's role as a hedge against macroeconomic instability.</li>\n                </ul>\n            </div>\n            <div class="report-card">\n                <h3>Risk Assessment</h3>\n                <ul>\n                    <li><strong>Price Volatility:</strong> The market remains extremely volatile.</li>\n                    <li><strong>Regulatory Risk:</strong> Adverse enforcement actions or regulations could cause volatility.</li>\n                    <li><strong>Macro Factors:</strong> Persistent inflation or unexpected geopolitical events.</li>\n                    <li><strong>Liquidity Risk:</strong> Large leveraged contract liquidations could cause a domino effect.</li>\n                </ul>\n            </div>\n            <div class="report-card">\n                <h3>Possible Scenarios (Short-term: next few days to a week)</h3>\n                <ul>\n                    <li><strong>Bullish Scenario:</strong> Bitcoin holds above $115,000 and rises back above $120,000. Positive news from Ripple-SEC or an unexpected dovish statement from the Fed. Strong resurgence in ETF inflows. <strong>Probability:</strong> Medium-Low.</li>\n                    <li><strong>Neutral Scenario:</strong> Bitcoin consolidates within the $115,000 - $122,000 range. The market awaits macroeconomic data and regulatory news. Slightly reduced trading volume. <strong>Probability:</strong> Medium-High.</li>\n                    <li><strong>Bearish Scenario:</strong> Bitcoin breaks the $110,000 support level, potentially heading towards $105,000. Higher-than-expected inflation data or a hawkish statement from the Fed. Escalating geopolitical events or negative regulatory news. Significant ETF outflows. <strong>Probability:</strong> Medium.</li>\n                </ul>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id="self-validation-section" class="report-section">\n        <h2><i class="fas fa-check-circle" style="color: var(--positive-color);"></i> Validation Summary</h2>\n        <div class="table-container report-card">\n            <table class="crypto-table">\n                <thead>\n                    <tr>\n                        <th>Data / Metric</th>\n                        <th>Reported Value</th>\n                        <th>Real-time Value</th>\n                        <th>Deviation</th>\n                        <th>Source (Report Value)</th>\n                        <th>Status</th>\n                    </tr>\n                </thead>\n                <tbody>\n                    <tr>\n                        <td data-label="Data / Metric">BTC Price</td>\n                        <td data-label="Reported Value">$119,118</td>\n                        <td data-label="Real-time Value">$119,118</td>\n                        <td data-label="Deviation">0%</td>\n                        <td data-label="Source (Report Value)">Real-time Dashboard</td>\n                        <td data-label="Status" style="color: var(--positive-color);">✅</td>\n                    </tr>\n                    <tr>\n                        <td data-label="Data / Metric">24h Change</td>\n                        <td data-label="Reported Value">-3.49%</td>\n                        <td data-label="Real-time Value">-3.49%</td>\n                   